wc / worldcommand             Adds a world command to the current recording

   Format:
      ;wc <cmd>               Adds a world command

   Notes:
      Adds a world command to the current recording, as if it had been sent to
         the world at this point in the recording.
      See the help for the ';record' command for more information about
         recordings.

   User commands:
      wc / worldcmd / worldcommand
